  "prompt": "Which is the best UPSC coaching centre in Coimbatore?",
  "response": "Choosing the best UPSC coaching center can be subjective and depends on various factors, such as teaching methodology, faculty experience, success rates, study materials, and student reviews. However, several coaching centers in Coimbatore are well-known for their UPSC preparation programs. Here are a few reputed ones:\n\n1. **Bharat IAS** - Known for its experienced faculty and comprehensive study materials.\n2. **Shankar IAS Academy** - Offers a structured curriculum and has a good track record of student success.\n3. **Civils360** - Provides personalized coaching and mentorship along with online resources.\n4. **ACE Academy** - Popular for its high-quality coaching and extensive study materials.\n\nIt's advisable to visit the centers, speak to faculty, and consider demo classes to determine which one suits your learning style and needs best. Also, checking the latest student reviews and success rates can help in making an informed decision.",
